  "debuggability": "Fixing https://crbug.com/507611251 is necessary to allow editing the full query in the styles pane and will be fixed before enabling this feature.\n\nIdentifying the matched container element does not support multiple containers, which means for the case below, there will not be a link to the matched container when --unknown is not the query that matches:\n\n@container --unknown, --found {}\n\nIn order to support that, the devtools protocol needs to pass which query in the @container rule that matched.\n",
